Name: ASCENT
checklistText:
<size=22>ASCENT</size>

1. Monitor Abort Light
2. Monitor Isolated Battery Voltage
3. Monitor Cabin Pressure
    a. Will go from 15 to 5.5
4. Monitor DC Voltage
5. Monitor DC Ammeter
6. Monitor AC Voltage

<size=20>At Engine Cutoff:</size>
	If Redstone Rocket Launch:
		Start REDSTONE Ascent Checklist
	If Atlas Rocket Launch:
		Start BECO Checklist
